==English==
===Etymology===
From Old French ''[[incredulité]]'', which comes from Latin ''[[incredulitas]]''

===Noun===
'''incredulity'''
# [[doubt|Doubt]] about the [[truth]] of something; [[unwillingness]] to [[believe]]; [[disbelief]].
# ''(rare)'' Religious disbelief.

